org.apache.hc.core5.reactor

Class AbstractIOEventHandler<T>

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.apache.hc.core5.reactor.AbstractIOEventHandler<T>
  • Type Parameters:
    T - the connection type.
    All Implemented Interfaces:
    IOEventHandler
    Direct Known Subclasses:
    DefaultHttpClientIOEventHandler, DefaultHttpServerIOEventHandler

    public abstract class AbstractIOEventHandler<T>
extends Object
implements IOEventHandler
    Abstract IOEventHandler implementation that supports both plain (non-encrypted) and SSL encrypted HTTP connections.
    Since:
    4.2
